{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Das <strong><code>FormData</code></strong>-Interface ermöglicht das einfache Erstellen eines Objektes bestehend aus&nbsp;Schlüssel/Werte-Paaren, welche Formular-Felder und ihre Werte repräsentieren. Dieses Objekt kann leicht durch das Aufrufen der <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/send\"><code>XMLHttpRequest.send()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Methode abgeschickt werden. Es&nbsp;verwendet das gleiche Format wie ein HTML-Formular, dessen Kodierung auf <code>\"multipart/form-data\"</code> gesetzt wurde.</p>\n\n<p>Ein Objekt, dass FormData implementiert, kann direkt in den <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/for...of\"><code>for...of</code></a> Strukturen benutzt werden, statt <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zu verwenden: <code>for (var p of myFormData)</code> ist identisch zu <code>for (var p of myFormData.entries())</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Dieses Feature ist in &nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>&nbsp;verfügbar.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"konstruktor","title":"Konstruktor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"formdata\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\" title=\"FormData()\"><code>FormData()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Erzeugt ein neues <code>FormData</code>-Objekt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"formdata.append_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>FormData.append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Fügt den Wert&nbsp;an den&nbsp;Wert eines&nbsp;bestehenden Schlüssel/Wert-Paares&nbsp;in einem <code>FormData</code>-Objekt an, oder fügt den Schlüssel mit dem Wert hinzu hinzu, falls dieser nicht vorhanden ist.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.delete_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>FormData.delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Löscht ein Schlüssel/Wert-Paar&nbsp;aus einem <code>FormData</code>-Objekt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.entries_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>FormData.entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> zurück, welcher das Iterieren über alle Schlüssel/Wert-Paare ermöglicht.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.get\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>FormData.get()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt den ersten Wert zurück, welcher dem gegebenen&nbsp;Schlüssel in dem <code>FormData</code>-Objekt zugeordnet ist.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.getall\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>FormData.getAll()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Erstellt ein Array, welches alle dem gegebenen Schlüssel zugeordneten Werte enthält.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.has_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>FormData.has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen boolean zurück, welcher Auskunft über das Vorhandenseins des gegeben Schlüssels im <code>FormData</code>-Objekt gibt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.keys_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>FormData.keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> zurück, welcher das Iterieren über alle Schlüssel der Schlüssel/Wert-Paare ermöglicht.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.set_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>FormData.set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Ersetzt den Wert für einen bestimmten Schlüssel im <code>FormData</code>-Objekt, oder legt das Schlüssel/Wert-Paar an, sollte der Schlüssel noch nicht existieren.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formdata.values_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>FormData.values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a> zurück, welcher das Iterieren über alle Werte der Schlüsselpaare ermöglicht.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-formdata\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'FormData' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>FormData definiert in XHR Spezifikation</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.FormData","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest benutzen</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\">FormData-Objekte benutzen</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Konstruktor","id":"konstruktor"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das FormData-Interface ermöglicht das einfache Erstellen eines Objektes bestehend aus Schlüssel/Werte-Paaren, welche Formular-Felder und ihre Werte repräsentieren. Dieses Objekt kann leicht durch das Aufrufen der XMLHttpRequest.send() (en-US) Methode abgeschickt werden. Es verwendet das gleiche Format wie ein HTML-Formular, dessen Kodierung auf \"multipart/form-data\" gesetzt wurde.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"FormData","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/formdata","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/formdata/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData","title":"FormData"}],"pageTitle":"FormData - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}